Objective

Identify non-OTP legal entities with transaction activity and business potential.

Key signals

• Employees (NB_EMPL)
• Engagement score (PRIMARY_SCORE)
• Expected income (INCOME, SAP)

Use case

Targeted ZKP offering to high-potential non-clients.

⬜ ПРАВА ЧАСТИНА (≈65%)
Client funnel

k companies → 7 potentially involved

Applied filters

• NB_EMPL > 1
• PRIMARY_SCORE > 25%
• INCOME > UAH

Engagement segmentation

High:  clients ·  avg
Medium:  clients · k UAH avg
Low:  clients ·k UAH avg

Result (1 рядок, жирним)

